{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br> <strong>Ghost Janitors</strong> is a 1-4 player co-op horror game where you and your friends clean haunted locations. What starts as a simple job quickly turns into a terrifying fight against eerie ghosts and dark secrets. Stay brave, work together, and scrub away the supernatural\u2014<strong>if you dare</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/TASKS.png?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Just do your job. Clean up the house with your team, get out and get rewarded for each task you complete.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newCleaning.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/STAYINTHELIGHT.png?t=1738251526\" />Remember, keep the generator and lights on all the time and stay in the light. We're pretty sure nothing bad is in the shadows, but <strong>it's better to be safe</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newGenerator.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/RANDOMIZED_AI.png?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every playthrough has a unique experience; Ghost Janitors introduces randomized AI, tasks, sounds, jumpscares, and more, delivering dynamic and <strong>unpredictable gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newJumpscare.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/PROGRESSION-new.png?t=1738251526\" />Dedication pays off, as the game rewards your progress with unlockable content. Discover new maps with captivating backstories, advanced equipment to enhance your cleaning efficiency, and a range of cosmetics to personalize your character..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newProgresion.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/FEATURES.png?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ghost Janitors boasts impressive graphics, heart-stopping jumpscares, and immersive 3D audio, creating a truly chilling atmosphere. Engage in proximity voice chat to share the terror with your friends in real time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newFeatures.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're seeking a horror game that combines thrills and entertainment, <strong>Ghost Janitors is a must-play</strong>. Gather your team, equip yourselves, and let's conquer the haunted challenge together!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"It's just the beginning","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772990/5f0aa0a82adacb12503cee8cfa8c15116f695089.jpg"},{"name":"Crimsonwood House","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772990/f59eed816ee677741e38a6a8acae5a62bb2912f3.jpg"},{"name":"Ravenwood Manor","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2772990/d393f