amstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newJumpscare.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/PROGRESSION-new.png?t=1738251526\" />Dedication pays off, as the game rewards your progress with unlockable content. Discover new maps with captivating backstories, advanced equipment to enhance your cleaning efficiency, and a range of cosmetics to personalize your character..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newProgresion.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/FEATURES.png?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ghost Janitors boasts impressive graphics, heart-stopping jumpscares, and immersive 3D audio, creating a truly chilling atmosphere. Engage in proximity voice chat to share the terror with your friends in real time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/extras/newFeatures.gif?t=1738251526\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're seeking a horror game that combines thrills and entertainment, <strong>Ghost Janitors is a must-play</strong>. Gather your team, equip yourselves, and let's conquer the haunted challenge together!</p>","developers":["Interactive Wave Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772990/header.jpg?t=1738251526","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recomme